semantic-search.error.title.value: Our search service is temporarily down.
semantic-search.error.title.comment: Title for the error message shown when semantic search failed.

semantic-search.error.text.value: We are working to resolve the issue.
semantic-search.error.text.comment: Body for the error message shown when semantic search failed.

semantic-search.no-results.comment: Message shown when semantic search returns no results. The {query} placeholder shows the search term entered by the user.

semantic-search.label.comment: Label for the input box that is used in semantic search.

semantic-search.placeholder.comment: Placeholder in the input box that is used in semantic search.

semantic-search.id.comment: Label of column that contains ID of the search results object.

semantic-search.tags.comment: Label of column that contains tags of the search results object.

semantic-search.match.comment: Label showing match percentage in search results. The {score} placeholder displays the relevance score as a number.

semantic-search.previous-search.comment: Area-label for the search history icon.

semantic-search.date.at.comment: Label for the date range filter identifying hour. Example: Today at 4:30.

semantic-search.ask.ai.assistant.comment: Button label for the ask ai assistant feature. This button is on search results list on bottom of drop down.

gs.date.today.comment: Label for the current day in date filters and selectors.

gs.date.yesterday.comment: Label for the day before today in date filters and selectors.
